and I'll grant you one in return.

570
00:36:22,732 --> 00:36:23,651
I pay each time.

571
00:36:23,972 --> 00:36:24,972
Why so calculative?

572
00:36:25,091 --> 00:36:26,011
Because I don't want

573
00:36:26,011 --> 00:36:27,211
to get entangled with you.

574
00:36:27,691 --> 00:36:29,131
Fine, as you say.

575
00:36:29,372 --> 00:36:30,332
Have you decided?

576
00:36:31,571 --> 00:36:32,932
What's your request this time?

577
00:36:35,611 --> 00:36:36,372
I've decided.

578
00:36:36,772 --> 00:36:38,571
Add me on WeChat. Scan my code.

579
00:36:44,571 --> 00:36:46,051
What brings you here today?

580
00:36:47,171 --> 00:36:49,772
I tried a braised dish spot
last night and found it good.

581
00:36:50,091 --> 00:36:51,452
The owner said they do breakfast,

582
00:36:51,452 --> 00:36:53,651
so I woke early to get you some.

583
00:36:54,252 --> 00:36:54,972
Try it first.

584
00:36:55,171 --> 00:36:56,091
I haven't tried it.

585
00:36:56,372 --> 00:36:58,091
Don't expect too much.
It might disappoint.

586
00:37:01,292 --> 00:37:02,131
Not bad.

587
00:37:02,372 --> 00:37:03,131
It's good?

588
00:37:03,491 --> 00:37:04,452
I'll buy more next time.

589
00:37:09,531 --> 00:37:12,051
I saw the report.
Our business are thriving.

590
00:37:12,611 --> 00:37:13,892
Don't just see the surface.

591
00:37:14,051 --> 00:37:15,252
Such a large group

592
00:37:15,412 --> 00:37:18,292
has countless trivial matters
beneath your notice.

593
00:37:18,732 --> 00:37:20,011
Don't focus only on now either.

594
00:37:20,292 --> 00:37:22,211
The future remains uncertain.

595
00:37:23,051 --> 00:37:24,491
If Roadsound's competitors

596
00:37:24,611 --> 00:37:26,651
had half your crisis awareness,

597
00:37:26,772 --> 00:37:28,611
they wouldn't have stayed
underfoot forever.

598
00:37:30,091 --> 00:37:32,651
You think these internal
and external troubles are imaginary?

599
00:37:34,892 --> 00:37:36,091
That's why I brought breakfast

600
00:37:36,292 --> 00:37:37,332
to ease your mind.

601
00:37:40,412 --> 00:37:41,491
I heard the other day

602
00:37:42,171 --> 00:37:43,252
Xiong caught someone.

603
00:37:43,252 --> 00:37:44,011
What happened?

604
00:37:50,531 --> 00:37:52,892
I know you want to help me,

605
00:37:53,211 --> 00:37:54,892
but some grassroots matters

606
00:37:55,171 --> 00:37:56,772
are better left untouched.

607
00:37:56,852 --> 00:37:57,611
Understood.

608
00:38:01,491 --> 00:38:02,812
The schedule is tight today.

609
00:38:03,211 --> 00:38:05,452
I need to visit the farm
before heading to the office.

610
00:38:06,651 --> 00:38:08,332
You even personally
oversee the planting?

611
00:38:08,611 --> 00:38:10,452
I need to check. I can't rest easy.

612
00:38:39,091 --> 00:38:40,732
Anyone here?

613
00:39:01,611 --> 00:39:04,972
Speak up now if you want less suffering.

614
00:39:08,531 --> 00:39:09,812
I'm old.

615
00:39:10,412 --> 00:39:11,452
I can't handle turmoil.

616
00:39:11,772 --> 00:39:12,772
Let's talk civilly.

617
00:39:16,051 --> 00:39:17,852
Where's the base
of South Mountain Hunters?

618
00:39:18,131 --> 00:39:19,171
How many members in total?

619
00:39:19,892 --> 00:39:21,972
What's your next action plan?

620
00:39:23,292 --> 00:39:24,011
The base...

621
00:39:25,292 --> 00:39:27,292
The base is at the South Heavenly Gate.

622
00:39:28,211 --> 00:39:31,691
Their numbers are hundreds of thousands,
and they are from a celestial army.

623
00:39:32,372 --> 00:39:36,292
And they plan to descend
to eradicate demons and monsters.

624
00:39:41,211 --> 00:39:42,372
Bad with essay questions?

625
00:39:42,852 --> 00:39:44,332
Then we'll make it multiple choice.

626
00:39:45,651 --> 00:39:46,732
How do you want to die?

627
00:39:47,412 --> 00:39:49,332
Bleed out? Heart extraction?

628
00:39:49,651 --> 00:39:51,011
Or live burial?

629
00:39:51,372 --> 00:39:53,812
If you'd brought Mrs. Hua with you,

630
00:39:54,412 --> 00:39:56,051
I'd choose live burial.

631
00:39:57,211 --> 00:39:59,131
We couldn't be together in life.

632
00:39:59,531 --> 00:40:00,932
Sharing a grave in death

633
00:40:01,051 --> 00:40:03,091
would fulfill my wish.

634
00:40:03,332 --> 00:40:04,972
That woman in the hospital

635
00:40:05,651 --> 00:40:06,611
is in such bad shape.

636
00:40:07,772 --> 00:40:09,892
She'll never speak again.

637
00:40:23,211 --> 00:40:24,531
He's quite spirited.

638
00:40:26,171 --> 00:40:27,252
Calm him down.

639
00:40:38,852 --> 00:40:39,812
Long time no see.

640
00:40:39,892 --> 00:40:41,211
Who are you?

641
00:40:42,372 --> 00:40:43,491
Twenty years ago,

642
00:40:43,932 --> 00:40:44,772
I offended you.

643
00:40:45,932 --> 00:40:46,732
Who?

644
00:40:49,611 --> 00:40:51,372
Don't tell me you're holding a grudge,

645
00:40:52,732 --> 00:40:54,732
wanting me to repay you with a leg?

646
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:14,343
(Greenhouse)

647
00:41:25,372 --> 00:41:27,292
Don't be fooled
by his usual carefree demeanor.

648
00:41:27,812 --> 00:41:29,772
He definitely has his own thoughts.

649
00:41:30,171 --> 00:41:31,491
He just buries them well.

650
00:41:32,491 --> 00:41:34,051
It's fine if it's not a deal-breaker.

651
00:41:34,651 --> 00:41:36,011
It's been many years.

652
00:41:36,772 --> 00:41:38,531
This whole mother-and-son-bond act

653
00:41:39,011 --> 00:41:41,091
has to continue, doesn't it?

654
00:41:41,412 --> 00:41:42,531
No matter what,

655
00:41:42,972 --> 00:41:44,892
Yan Tuo is my own son.

656
00:41:46,412 --> 00:41:48,892
Wake the old man below
and resume interrogation.

657
00:41:49,452 --> 00:41:51,452
We must extract information
about the Mad Blade.

658
00:41:51,611 --> 00:41:52,772
Understood. We'll handle it.

659
00:42:13,812 --> 00:42:14,651
(Lin Ling?)

660
00:42:17,011 --> 00:42:17,732
(Lin Ling?)

661
00:42:19,732 --> 00:42:21,171
(Where are you? Come out.)

662
00:42:22,531 --> 00:42:23,332
(Lin Ling.)

663
00:42:25,091 --> 00:42:25,892
(Lin Ling?)

664
00:42:27,972 --> 00:42:29,171
(Come out now.)

665
00:42:29,892 --> 00:42:30,852
(This is not fun.)

666
00:42:30,932 --> 00:42:32,611
(Ms. Lin will scold us
if she finds out.)

667
00:42:35,252 --> 00:42:36,011
(Lin Ling?)

668
00:42:36,691 --> 00:42:37,452
(Lin Ling?)

669
00:42:40,292 --> 00:42:40,972
(Lin Ling?)

670
00:43:08,976 --> 00:43:11,664
(Toxic and Hazardous)

671
00:43:39,312 --> 00:43:40,200
Lin Xirou.

672
00:43:43,560 --> 00:43:45,880
This humanoid Earth Fiend
and the Roadsound Group

673
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:47,280
must be closely connected.

674
00:43:47,600 --> 00:43:49,080
This intel is crucial.

675
00:43:49,160 --> 00:43:50,600
We'll investigate immediately.

676
00:43:51,160 --> 00:43:51,800
Thank you.

677
00:43:52,600 --> 00:43:53,640
How's Sun Zhou?

678
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:56,880
Overcast skies may make us

679
00:43:57,760 --> 00:43:58,720
miss the window.

680
00:43:59,200 --> 00:44:00,120
Do what you can.

681
00:44:00,320 --> 00:44:02,560
If even heaven won't save him,

682
00:44:02,920 --> 00:44:03,880
we can't help with that.

683
00:44:04,400 --> 00:44:05,200
Then

684
00:44:05,520 --> 00:44:07,840
we'll have to banish him to Golden Gate

685
00:44:08,000 --> 00:44:09,160
by Hunters' rules.

686
00:44:10,240 --> 00:44:11,680
Those wounded by Earth Fiends before

687
00:44:11,760 --> 00:44:13,800
and became infected
without timely fire purification

688
00:44:13,880 --> 00:44:15,120
were all Hunters

689
00:44:15,560 --> 00:44:17,040
who vowed to accept this fate.

690
00:44:17,040 --> 00:44:18,240
They were all prepared.

691
00:44:18,560 --> 00:44:20,080
But Sun Zhou is a civilian.

692
00:44:22,640 --> 00:44:23,840
For him,

693
00:44:24,720 --> 00:44:25,800
it's too cruel.

694
00:44:25,808 --> 00:44:26,465
Of course.

695
00:44:27,240 --> 00:44:28,880
I'll explore alternatives.

696
00:44:31,280 --> 00:44:35,600
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

697
00:44:38,880 --> 00:44:39,800
Are you still there?

698
00:44:40,528 --> 00:44:40,968
Yes.

699
00:44:41,720 --> 00:44:42,680
Speaking of which,

700
00:44:43,400 --> 00:44:45,800
about the informant you mentioned,
who tipped you off

701
00:44:45,960 --> 00:44:47,840
about Lin Xirou and the Roadsound Group,

702
00:44:48,048 --> 00:44:49,090
who is he?

703
00:44:49,600 --> 00:44:50,720
You think he's unreliable?

704
00:44:50,840 --> 00:44:52,520
I'm worried for your safety.

705
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:54,120
How did you connect with him?

706
00:44:56,240 --> 00:44:57,720
Maybe my unique constitution

707
00:44:57,920 --> 00:45:00,000
attracts oddities.

708
00:45:01,640 --> 00:45:03,520
We've got plenty of oddities here too.

709
00:45:04,360 --> 00:45:07,320
They're all here at the hospital
keeping watch over Mrs. Hua.

710
00:45:07,880 --> 00:45:10,160
I gotta go. It's starting up again.

711
00:45:10,768 --> 00:45:11,284
Okay.

712
00:45:15,904 --> 00:45:20,264
♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

713
00:45:20,264 --> 00:45:24,584
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

714
00:45:24,584 --> 00:45:29,024
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

715
00:45:29,024 --> 00:45:31,464
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

716
00:45:31,464 --> 00:45:35,544
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

717
00:45:35,544 --> 00:45:39,904
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

718
00:45:39,904 --> 00:45:44,264
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

719
00:45:44,264 --> 00:45:48,624
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

720
00:45:48,624 --> 00:45:52,984
♪Heaven-kindled flames are different♪

721
00:45:52,984 --> 00:45:57,264
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

722
00:45:57,264 --> 00:46:01,824
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

723
00:46:01,824 --> 00:46:09,544
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪
